  "long_description": "### AKA\n* Chicago\n* Quota Game\n### Description\nA quota/Stableford scoring game with gross skins.\n\n### Stableford Points (Gross)\n* Double Eagle (albatross): 6 points\n* Eagle: 4 points\n* Birdie: 3 points\n* Par: 2 points\n* Bogey: 1 point\n* Double bogey or worse: 0 points\n\n### Quota System\nEach player's quota = par - handicap strokes received.\n* Front/Back split: If quota is odd, add +1 to the easier nine (by rating)\n* Performance = Stableford points - quota (e.g., 18 points vs 14 quota = +4)\n\n### Skins (Gross)\n* Gross birdie or better wins the skin\n* Eagles override birdies on the same hole\n* One winner per hole (no carryovers)\n\n### Settlement\n* 75% of pot: Stableford (split into front/back/overall thirds)\n* 25% of pot: Gross skins\n* Each Stableford third pays 1st/2nd/3rd by quota performance\n",
